target:
1/2 mina of refined silver, its import duty added, its transport tariff paid, for Šarrat-Ištar;
5 10 shekels of refined silver from my votive offerings;
5 shekels of refined silver belonging to Šišahšušar for the purchase of a ring;
5 shekels of silver for his sacrifices for Kurub-Ištar;
5 shekels of silver belonging to Aššur-nēmedi for Šarrat-Ištar;
1 1/2 shekel for his sheep-all this I entrusted to Ennam-Aššur son of Iddin-Suen.
Witnessed by Iddin-abum; witnessed by Annina; witnessed by Annina son of Puzur-Anna
